HEADWORD: Engaol
<hw>En*gaol"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>gaol</ets>: cf. OF. <ets>engaoler</ets>,
<ets>engeoler</ets>. See <er>Gaol</er>, and cf. <er>Enjail</er>.]</ety>
<def>To put in jail; to imprison.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
